articles.author: Al Jazeera
articles.title: African Union suspends Gabon’s membership after military coup - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: The body said it ‘strongly condemns the military takeover’ that resulted in the ouster of President Ali Bongo Ondimba.
articles.content:
The African Unions Peace and Security Council said it has decided to immediately suspend Gabon following the military coup in the country this week.
